    <!-- About Section -->
    <section id="about" class="about-section section-padding">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title wow fadeInUp">About Me</h2>

        <div class="row">

          <div class="col-md-4 col-md-push-8">
            <div class="biography">
              <div class="myphoto">
                <img src="assets/images/pro-bw.jpg" alt="">
              </div>
              <ul>
                <li><strong>Name:</strong> Bob Steeger</li>
                <!-- <li><strong>Date of birth:</strong> 05 Dec 1993</li> -->
                <li><strong>Address:</strong> Northern Virginia, USA</li>
                <li><strong>Nationality:</strong> American</li>
                <li><strong>Phone:</strong> (703) 665-9843</li>
                <li><strong>Email:</strong> mail@bobsteeger.com</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div> <!-- col-md-4 -->

          <div class="col-md-8 col-md-pull-4">
            <div class="short-info wow fadeInUp">
              <h3>Summary</h3>
              <p>Internet and business professional providing vision, product development and management of innovative experiences and services in ecommerce and online delivery.  Combine partnership building and technical expertise with design acumen and customer-facing strengths to produce successful solutions.  Passionate about Product Management, Life Long Learning and all things Data.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="short-info wow fadeInUp">
              <h3>What I Do ?</h3>
              <p>My forte is using technology to solve problems, satisfy customer and consumer needs, and creating efficiencies in any type of process.  I combine partnership building and technical expertise with design acumen and customer-facing strengths to produce successful solutions.  With 10 years experience in Product Management, and 5 years in Program Management I balance creativity with structure and planning to create both effective and efficient teams.  I have an extensive and progressive background in technology encompassing the entire IT stack and have worked in and with nearly every business operation group.
</p>

              <ul class="list-check">
                <li>Vision & Strategy Development</li>
                <li>Development - Agile, SCRUM, Kanban</li>
                <li>Market Analysis & Positioning</li>
                <li>Program & Project Management</li>
                <li>Product & Portfolio Management</li>
                <li>Product Marketing & Distribution</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="my-signature">
              <img src="assets/images/sign.png" alt="">
            </div>

            <div class="download-button">
              <a class="btn btn-info btn-lg" href="#contact"><i class="fa fa-paper-plane"></i>Send me message</a>
              <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="./Bob_Steeger_Resume.pdf"><i class="fa fa-download"></i>download my resume</a>
            </div>
          </div>


