                                            <p>Defined product strategy, requirements and roadmaps to plan releases / sprints for multiple $10M+ eCommerce websites. Implemented standardized processes for Product team.  Collaborated with sales teams on strategy, presentations, and customer visits to define and deliver premium features.</p>
